headline: Snavely Forest Products Announces Strategic Partnership with Weyerhaeuser to Expand Engineered Wood Offerings
summary: Snavely Forest Products ("Snavely"), a wholly-owned subsidiary of MacArthur Company and a leader in the wholesale building materials industry, is proud to announce a strategic partnership with Weyerhaeuser, manufacturer of Trus Joist engineered wood products. This collaboration will enhance Snavely's ability to serve professional builders and dealers with best-in-class structural framing solutions across key markets.
